      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's intense and really hits that period tone. To wrap up the scene, could you have him conclude the speech by addressing the physical and mental differences he perceives between his men and the locals? Like, why he feels it's actually a natural or even a moral necessity for his people to take charge based on those inherent qualities.",
